title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Jets quarterback Ken O'Brien was acquitted of similar charges arising out of a bruising melee by the jury.” [From the New York Post, 13 September 1984. Submitted by Carol Ann Hilton, Staten Island, New York.]
